446
00:31:59,563 --> 00:32:01,683
Congratulations on having a son.

447
00:32:01,683 --> 00:32:02,720
Congratulations, Master.

448
00:32:08,736 --> 00:32:12,283
[Pei's Mansion]

449
00:32:12,283 --> 00:32:13,312
Sanlang,

450
00:32:13,843 --> 00:32:15,683
the Master knows you love wine.

451
00:32:17,803 --> 00:32:18,843
Fine wines are here.

452
00:32:19,643 --> 00:32:22,203
Silang,
the Master knows you're partial to beef.

453
00:32:22,883 --> 00:32:24,163
Have a taste of these.

454
00:32:26,203 --> 00:32:29,163
The Master and the Madam have been married
for more than a decade.

455
00:32:29,163 --> 00:32:30,883
Now, finally they're blessed with an heir.

456
00:32:31,643 --> 00:32:33,440
Let's drink together to celebrate.

457
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,624
Cheng,

458
00:32:34,624 --> 00:32:35,783
over these years,

459
00:32:35,783 --> 00:32:39,203
the Deputy Protector-General has promoted education
and benevolent governance in Xizhou.

460
00:32:39,203 --> 00:32:40,483
He finally moved God

461
00:32:41,203 --> 00:32:42,272
and was rewarded.

462
00:32:42,883 --> 00:32:44,083
Let's toast the Deputy Protector-General.

463
00:32:44,083 --> 00:32:45,152
Let's toast him.

464
00:32:50,203 --> 00:32:52,483
The Master once wrote a poem for this wine.

465
00:32:52,483 --> 00:32:53,803
This really is a fine wine.

466
00:32:53,803 --> 00:32:56,803
At the pavilion we bid our farewells.

467
00:32:59,363 --> 00:33:02,243
Bees inebriated, wings too heavy to lift.

468
00:33:03,043 --> 00:33:05,723
Peace and prosperity across the lands.

469
00:33:07,403 --> 00:33:10,523
O, what fine wine.

470
