Fine wine.

471
00:33:12,323 --> 00:33:13,376
Drink.

472
00:33:13,923 --> 00:33:14,923
Fine wine.

473
00:33:29,203 --> 00:33:30,483
How is the baby today?

474
00:33:31,843 --> 00:33:32,896
He's good.

475
00:34:05,523 --> 00:34:06,683
Who sent this?

476
00:34:07,443 --> 00:34:08,763
Though the thing is ordinary,

477
00:34:09,323 --> 00:34:11,043
the thought behind it is estimable.

478
00:34:12,403 --> 00:34:14,443
It is master Fang and lady Liu.

479
00:34:15,563 --> 00:34:16,923
How nice of them to send this.

480
00:34:17,523 --> 00:34:18,903
Are they doing well now?

481
00:34:18,903 --> 00:34:20,363
How did it get sent here?

482
00:34:23,683 --> 00:34:24,883
Lie did a credit,

483
00:34:26,003 --> 00:34:27,323
and he doesn't vie for power,

484
00:34:28,923 --> 00:34:30,443
so he can have a peaceful life

485
00:34:30,443 --> 00:34:31,683
under Ashina Duzhi's control.

486
00:34:32,883 --> 00:34:34,403
I have my own ways to contact him.

487
00:34:34,403 --> 00:34:35,680
You don't have to worry.

488
00:34:37,792 --> 00:34:38,963
Things in the world are unpredictable,

489
00:34:39,483 --> 00:34:40,803
but there's still hope.

490
00:34:41,483 --> 00:34:42,496
I believe that one day,

491
00:34:43,043 --> 00:34:45,483
Master Fang will certainly bring lady Liu

492
00:34:45,483 --> 00:34:47,043
back upright and aboveboard.

493
00:34:57,723 --> 00:34:58,803
Madam Yang has sent a letter.

494
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:15,488
[Madam Yang's Letter]

495
00:35:17,883 --> 00:35:19,483
Today, the appointment was proclaimed.

496
00:35:20,832 --> 00:35:21,963
I am appointed

497
00:35:23,043 --> 00:35:24,083
as the Vice Minister of Foreign Affairs.

498
00:35:27,323 --> 00:35:28,363
In the end,

499
00:35:29,683 --> 00:35:30,843
we still must return to Chang'an.

500
00:36:32,723 --> 00:36:33,728
Liuli,

501
00:36:37,083 --> 00:36:38,963
if none of you go back,

502
00:36:40,003 --> 00:36:41,003
how good that would be?

503
00:36:43,243 --> 00:36:44,323
Chongyu once said

504
00:36:45,483 --> 00:36:46,563
Chang'an

505
00:36:47,923 --> 00:36:49,163
was the least free place

506
00:36:50,123 --> 00:36:51,923
in the world.

507
00:36:55,403 --> 00:36:56,723
He was right.

508
00:36:58,883 --> 00:37:00,883
People can find supreme power

509
00:37:00,883 --> 00:37:02,283
and wealth there,

510
00:37:03,683 --> 00:37:05,863
and it draws everyone

511
00:37:05,863 --> 00:37:07,163
under its sway.

512
00:37:09,243 --> 00:37:10,763
No matter how much I want,

513
00:37:13,643 --> 00:37:15,763
I ultimately can no longer stay by his side.

514
00:37:18,848 --> 00:37:19,872
Liuli,

515
00:37:20,883 --> 00:37:22,483
in the future,

516
00:37:23,163 --> 00:37:24,243
could you and your husband

517
00:37:26,403 --> 00:37:28,483
take care of Chongyu for me in Chang'an?

518
00:37:31,683 --> 00:37:33,563
Although he has never told me,

519
00:37:34,203 --> 00:37:35,283
I know

520
00:37:37,203 --> 00:37:39,043
he is afraid of going to that place,

521
00:37:40,843 --> 00:37:42,283
but he has no way.

522
00:37:45,723 --> 00:37:46,944
Yunyi.

523
00:37:49,003 --> 00:37:50,016
Liuli,

524
00:37:51,923 --> 00:37:53,683
I really admire you and your husband.

525
00:37:54,723 --> 00:37:56,363
Wherever you are,

526
00:37:57,363 --> 00:37:58,803
whatever obstacles you face,

527
00:38:00,083 --> 00:38:01,683
you always walk hand in hand,

528
00:38:02,803 --> 00:38:03,963
never parting.

529
00:38:09,083 --> 00:38:10,112
How great.

530
00:39:28,483 --> 00:39:30,443
How could you?

531
00:39:30,443 --> 00:39:31,552
Liuli,

532
00:39:32,203 --> 00:39:33,643
from the moment I saw you today,

533
00:39:34,403 --> 00:39:36,043
I realized that I was terribly wrong,

534
00:39:36,923 --> 00:39:38,283
but I never imagined

535
00:39:39,803 --> 00:39:41,283
that I had made such grave mistakes.

536
00:39:42,624 --> 00:39:43,683
You just wait

537
00:39:44,323 --> 00:39:45,903
and see how I'll settle the score with you

538
00:39:45,903 --> 00:39:47,163
after I leave here.

539
00:39:48,003 --> 00:39:49,443
Liuli!

540
00:39:49,443 --> 00:39:50,563
There was such a moment

541
00:39:51,323 --> 00:39:52,563
when I was really afraid of losing you.

542
00:39:53,163 --> 00:39:54,343
Don't talk nonsense.

543
00:39:54,343 --> 00:39:55,803
I swear

544
00:39:55,803 --> 00:39:57,943
I'm sticking with you for life.

545
00:39:57,943 --> 00:40:00,603
Even if I become an old woman
with a face full of wrinkles,

546
00:40:00,603 --> 00:40:02,003
don't even think about getting rid of me.

547
00:40:03,483 --> 00:40:04,563
This is our home.

548
00:40:05,723 --> 00:40:08,403
This is the first courtyard
we bought ourselves.

549
00:40:09,163 --> 00:40:10,523
No schemes,

550
00:40:11,083 --> 00:40:12,483
